&lt;p&gt;Salary: £7,508 to £7,959 depending on experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hourly Rate: £9.00 to £9.54&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Windmill Practice would like to expand its Reception Team with the appointment of an additional receptionist&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Practice Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Well organised and reputable GMS Practice, rated good in last CQC inspection , located within Sneinton Health Centre providing high quality and innovative care to a wide range of patients including the most vulnerable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10 GPs, 3 Practice Nurse Prescribers, 2 Practice Nurses, 2 Healthcare Assistants and 15 Administrative Support Staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GP Registrar training practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Patient List size – circa 9,600&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clinical System – TPP Systm One&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and people skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A friendly and welcoming manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Significant experience of working with the public in a reception environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position is for 16 hours a week working from 1.00 pm to 4.00pm Monday, Tuesday, Thursday and Friday and 1.00pm to 5.00pm on a Wednesday &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The flexibility to provide cover for holidays/absence together with the occasional Saturday morning is also required. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants are asked not to reapply. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you require any additional information or to arrange an informal visit, do please contact Mark Ebb, Practice Manager on 0115 8838685 or at markebb@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
